Tim Sherwood takes on his friend Chris Ramsey when Aston Villa play Queens Park Rangers on Tuesday . 
  Ramsey was Sherwood's ally at Tottenham last season . 
  Villa lost 3-0 to Manchester United in the Premier League on Saturday . 
  Ramsey led QPR to a 4-1 win at West Bromwich Albion . 
  Rangers can move out of the relegation zone with a win at Villa Park . 
 